---
title: Caribbean Pulled Pork Bowl with Coconut Rice & Charred Pineapple Salsa
description: We’ve packed the signature flavours of the Caribbean into this pulled pork bowl with mild jerk seasoning and a tangy charred pineapple salsa, but we think the rich coconut rice on the side might just be the best bit!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/caribbean-pulled-pork-bowl-5d4e2fcd.jpg
